🔗 Colorless, Shapeless Orb - Gapingvoid 

We call it The Void. It’s where most work lives now. Transactional. Comfortable. Manageable. Forgettable. If you’ve ever wondered why our name is so weird, that’s it. We made it our business to kill it.&nbsp; 

👁️ Yes. Seperately - love their new home page.
